---
// Representative inner service page — demonstrates the inner-page template
// (page-hero + breadcrumbs + prose + CTA band) in the copied design system.
// Title/meta carried over verbatim from the live WordPress page.
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { business } from '../data/site';

const title = 'BEST Exterior Painters In Town | Exterior Painting Oklahoma City';
const description =
  'We provide exterior painting Oklahoma City can trust. Exterior house painting is a must to protect your home from the OKC weather. 5 Year warranty on our exterior work!';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> › Exterior Painting
      </nav>
      <h1>Exterior Painting Oklahoma City Homeowners Can Trust</h1>
      <p>
        Protect your home from Oklahoma's brutal sun, wind, and storms with a full-prep exterior
        repaint — backed by our 5-year written warranty.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="prose">
    <div class="container">
      <p>
        Your home's exterior takes a beating in Oklahoma. Between the relentless summer sun, hail,
        and temperature swings, paint that wasn't applied correctly will fade, peel, and crack in just
        a few years. That's why every exterior project we do starts with thorough prep — not a quick
        spray-and-go.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Exterior Painting Process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Wash &amp; prep:</strong> Pressure wash, scrape, sand, and remove all failing paint.</li>
        <li><strong>Repair:</strong> Caulk gaps, replace rotted wood, and spot-prime bare surfaces.</li>
        <li><strong>Prime:</strong> Bonding primer where it counts so the topcoat actually lasts.</li>
        <li><strong>Paint:</strong> Two coats of premium Sherwin-Williams Duration or Emerald.</li>
        <li><strong>Walkthrough:</strong> We don't call it done until you're happy with every detail.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Prep Matters in Oklahoma</h2>
      <p>
        Paint failure almost always comes down to prep, not the paint itself. Our crews take the time
        to do it right, which is how we can stand behind every exterior job with a 5-year warranty.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get a Free Exterior Painting Estimate</h2>
      <a href={business.phoneHref} class="cta-phone">Call {business.phoneDisplay}</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
